Where is the API access token located

To find your API Access Token, log in to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Then click on Tools - Resources - API Access Tokens. Here, you can click 'Generate token' to create your own API access token. Remember, this token is tied to your user ID and should not be shared with anyone else.
